    "7919047": {
      "title": "Cardioprotection by Klotho through downregulation of TRPC6 channels in the mouse heart",
      "abstract": "Mice that cannot produce the hormone Klotho show various aging-related phenotypes. Here, Xie and colleagues reveal that Klotho protects the heart of mice from stress-induced remodelling by inhibiting exocytosis of the TRPC6 ion channel in cardiomyocytes."
